    <section id="id-109820466968">
      <title>Why Do It?</title>
      <para id="id3828382">
        <quote display="block" id="idm511488">“Through careful instructional design, support, and guidance from the instructor, along with ongoing feedback from students to the instructor and from the instructor to the students, an online course can evolve into a robust, productive, and enjoyable learning community” (Kleinman, 2005, p.17).</quote>
      </para>
</section>
